description: Simply perfect sunlit one bed, plus den, corner unit on the 12th floor at the highly desired EchelonSeaport! Includes 1 valet garage parking, in-unit washer and dryer and on-floor additional storage. Unit is beautifully designed with floor to ceiling windows with owner added Hunter Douglas automated shades.Gorgeous, functional kitchen. Den allows for amazing workspace and seating area. Large bedroom and bathroom. Sophisticated bar space and hi-gloss white cabinetry complete the look! Water views inc.Logan Airport. Echelon Seaport is a full-service, luxury 24X7 concierge building with many amenities! Enjoy state-of-the art fitness center, three swimming pools including one indoor pool, spa, indoor basketball court, and yoga/pilates studio. Luxurious spaces to hold private parties. Live and enjoy all that the fabulous Seaport in Boston offers with a vast array of restaurants, shopping, and entertainment, incl.Trader Joe's and CVS. Excellent access to all major highways and transits.
